text: Rosalba stigmatifera is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1868. It is known from Panama and South America.BioLib.cz - Rosalba stigmatifera. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1868
title: Rosalba stigmatifera
